"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/228592","Department of Health","false","2015-03-24","<p>Data from November 2010 onwards is available in the NHS England Weekly A&amp;E Performance Reports, which are published online at:</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p><a href="http://www.england.nhs.uk/statistics/statistical-work-areas/ae-waiting-times-and-activity/" target="_blank">http://www.england.nhs.uk/statistics/statistical-work-areas/ae-waiting-times-and-activity/</a></p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p>Prior to this period, accident and emergency data was collected quarterly from 2001/02, which is available at:</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p><a href="http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20130107105354/http:/www.dh.gov.uk/en/Publicationsandstatistics/Statistics/Performancedataandstatistics/AccidentandEmergency/index.htm" target="_blank">http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20130107105354/http://www.dh.gov.uk/en/Publicationsandstatistics/Statistics/Performancedataandstatistics/AccidentandEmergency/index.htm</a></p><p> </p>","Battersea","Jane Ellison",,"2015-03-24T17:41:55.72Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/228592/answer","Biography information for Jane Ellison","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/228592/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/228592/answer",,,,,"17","Health","Health","2015-03-19","Accident and Emergency Departments: Blackpool","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, how many people attended at hospital A&E departments in the Blackpool NHS Trust area in each year from 2010 to 2015.","false","Biography information for Gordon Marsden","Blackpool South","Mr Gordon Marsden","228509"
