.uk/resources/228612/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2015-03-19","Passports","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, what the average length of time taken by the Passport Office to make a decision on renewal of an expired passport was in each year since 2010.","false","Biography information for Steve McCabe","Birmingham, Selly Oak","Steve McCabe","228340"
